      <![CDATA[If books were pills, <i>Alchemist</i> would be a sugarcoated placebo with no real effect. Say, a feel-good homily. I have never read a book as meretricious as this one. Many a reviewer has pointed out the problems with this 'celebrated' novel so I need not expend many words. Suffice it so say that this...]]>
